Name: 6th Dimension
About the game: The 6th Dimension is a first person single player riddle and puzzle solving game. You play as a traveler going through the 6th dimension. Inside the 6th dimension you will find different eco-systems you must traverse. You must find a way to get back to your dimension, in order to do this you must navigate all eco-systems within the 6th dimension and find all the sacred texts that will unlock the doors back to your reality. Once you find the text, you will have to do a series of riddles and puzzles in order to collect the sacred text from that eco-system. Let's hope you can make it back to reality.
